      • generateColumnMap

        ORMapInfo generateColumnMap(java.lang.Class<?> clazz)
        已过时。 It's suggested to use generateColumnMap(Class, String) instead
        generate one O-R mapping object, if the class class is mapped to more than one tables, return the first table
        参数:
        clazz - POJO class
        返回:
        mapping info

      • generateColumnMap

        ORMapInfo generateColumnMap(java.lang.Class<?> clazz,
                          java.lang.String tableName)
        generate mapping info of specified table
        参数:
        clazz - POJO class
        tableName - The specified table name, the first table's info will be returned if this parameter is null
        返回:
        mapping info
